snippet.title: Tank 1990 (FC · Famicom / NES) unlicensed Mod | 1-loop "Tank N" (setting 15-28) session for 1 Player
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMpNLYz8bcz1-i2vWxSEieQ?sub_confirmation=1 “Tank 1990 is a modification of BattleCity published by Yanshan Software in 1990. It is very common as a multicart game on various 8-bit Famiclone consoles. Here, you’ll encounter 108 stages in a loop for the N mode (setting 15-28).”


https://twitter.com/NenrikiGaming
